avdta.vehicle

Class PersonalVehicle

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.vehicle.Vehicle
      • avdta.vehicle.PersonalVehicle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Vehicle>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bus, MTPersonalVehicle

    public class PersonalVehicle
extends Vehicle
    This represents a privately-owned vehicle. PersonalVehicles depart at a predetermined time and travel from an origin Zone to a destination Zone.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
